    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This mid-engine masterpiece features a 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering linear power through a precision 6-speed manual transaxle. Meticulously preserved, it boasts a flawless Arctic Silver metallic finish and an interior devoid of bolster wear. Performance is sharpened by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Recent service includes a full borescope inspection, updated IMS bearing for peace of mind, and fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber on lightweight staggered alloys. A turn-key example of analog perfection with zero mechanical compromises.",
